{"tid":2459184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共開始心急要追數","createTime":"2021-03-24T04:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T06:00:11.000Z","uid":18679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"445f45736b4ee22693d9a85c916eebc6b77dbd78","tid":2459184,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:04:20.000Z","msg":"本港和澳門當局收到復星通知，進口的復必泰新冠疫苗封蓋包裝有瑕疵，為謹慎起見，港澳即時叫停接種。多間接種復必泰疫苗的社區接種中心外仍見有大批市民排隊，有市民按預約時間到場，才知道暫停接種，直言感到很錯愕「唔知咩事」。亦有市民知悉後稱，叫停是較安全做法，對復必泰仍有信心。<br />\n<br />\n係囉係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0df900c878ef7097db5754dbe4469a30fbe689e","tid":2459184,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:06:21.000Z","msg":"肥水不留別人田<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97672d766fa08f683d094dc43aef4a94fcd7c1a0","tid":2459184,"uid":160964,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港豬第2針要打科興了"},{"pid":"de140be125238e2058a9eb6deee2639115d70e15","tid":2459184,"uid":329977,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vTjOqq1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvTjOqq1.gif&h=d7139317&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9fa73c82ee45b528c0e3c0360eaf79dffac6622a","tid":2459184,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8507b22ec0a0a1f57edd573bba961e14a1b692a9","tid":2459184,"uid":45910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T04:14:41.000Z","msg":"強制溝針實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe23b71db16b65ca16722b4de1cedfe96e6979e4","tid":2459184,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislik